  "instructions": [
    "Cut the oyster mushrooms into 1-inch pieces and place them in a bowl.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together soy sauce, honey, rice vinegar, grated ginger, and olive oil to make the glaze.",
    "Add the minced garlic, chopped green onions, sesame seeds, salt, and black pepper to the bowl with the mushrooms and toss to combine.",
    "Thread the mushroom mixture onto skewers, leaving a small space between each piece.",
    "Preheat the air fryer to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Cook the skewers in the air fryer for 10-12 minutes, or until the mushrooms are tender and lightly caramelized.",
    "Brush the glaze over the mushrooms during the last 2 minutes of cooking.",
    "Serve immediately, garnished with additional green onions if desired."
  ],
